---
layout: layouts/base.njk
title: "Future Shock Media — Podcast & media network"
description: "Future Shock Media: boring on purpose. Podcasts and media with a retro-futuristic sensibility—signal without the noise."
ogTitle: "Future Shock Media"
ogDescription: "Boring on purpose. Podcasts and media with a retro-futuristic sensibility—signal without the noise."
---
{% import "macros/episode-card.njk" as ep %}

<section class="hero hero--cover" aria-label="Intro">
  <div class="hero-inner">
    <div class="hero-text">
      <h1><span class="hero-brand">{{ site.title }}</span></h1>
      <p class="hero-tagline">{{ site.subtitle }}</p>
      <div class="btn-group">
        <a href="/episodes/" class="btn btn-primary" data-testid="link-episodes">Browse episodes &rarr;</a>
        <a href="/guest-request/" class="btn btn-outline" data-testid="link-guest-request">Be a guest</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

{% set sortedEpisodes = episodes | sortEpisodesDesc %}
{% if sortedEpisodes.length %}
<section class="container home-section-flush">
  <div class="flex-between mb-6">
    <h2 class="section-title mb-0">Latest episodes</h2>
    <a href="/episodes/" class="btn btn-outline btn-sm">View all &rarr;</a>
  </div>
  <div class="card-list">
    {% for episode in sortedEpisodes %}
    {% if loop.index0 < 3 %}
    {{ ep.episodeCard(episode, clickable=true, truncateDesc=true) }}
    {% endif %}
    {% endfor %}
  </div>
</section>
{% endif %}

<section class="container home-section-flush">
  <div class="card brand-card">
    <div class="brand-card-inner">
      <div class="brand-card-deco" aria-hidden="true"></div>
      <div class="brand-card-text">
        <h2 class="font-bold heading-md">Why &ldquo;Future Shock&rdquo;?</h2>
        <p class="text-sm text-muted">Podcast and media for people who want signal without the noise. The name borrows the old idea of future shock &mdash; change moving faster than culture can absorb &mdash; and the work stays measured: clear, a bit retro-futurist, light on hype.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
